    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it a great choice for a daily driver. While the exterior paint and interior upholstery show some minor, expected signs of wear from regular use, the car remains clean and structurally sound. It\u2019s a solid, dependable vehicle that offers a great balance of quality and value.",
