    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The body has extensive rust, multiple dents, and the paint is failing. The interior is in bad shape with ripped seats and broken trim pieces. It has significant mechanical issues and requires major repairs to be roadworthy.",
