    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections. The exterior shows some clear coat peeling on the roof and a few minor door dings consistent with its age. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's side bolster, though all major electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it starts and runs fine, but it will likely need a brake service and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that just needs a little bit of attention to bring it back to its best.",
      "price": 19800.0,
